section2.text3: And my main inspiration is you.
section2.text4: I like to work with people and create something from zero what is going to stay forever on the human body. I do freehand and freestyle tattoos - it's about freedom and feeling.
section2.text5: Everyone has their own special energy's which i read in our first 15 min when we meet: how you smile, how you speak, how you feel yourself. There comes an image in my head where i already can see the future design for your project.

section4.text1: THE PROCESS FOR ME IS ALWAYS LIKE WE DANCE FEELING EACH OTHER AND THAT TIME COMES SOMETHING UNIQUE FOR YOU AND FOR ME.

section5.text5: Trust to the artist starts with trust in the world. My aim is to inspire faith in yourself, the future, and life itself through tattoos.
section5.text7: I want to deliver a message through my art that you are free and free always and everywhere. The choice is always yours.
